| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-5205 — Recovery Inhibition (dragonforce)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 8d2a0569-4df3-5cdf-9e39-f7160642092e"
